714761f-a.title: Manhattan: 88th Street - Park Avenue
714761f-a.text:
88th Street, at, adjoining, and west of the N.W. corner of Park Avenue, seen from across the excavation on the S.W. corner.
January 31, 1928.
P. L. Sperr.

722364f-a.title: Manhattan: Park Avenue - 88th Street
722364f-a.text:
1070 Park Avenue, on S. W. corner of 88th Street, a new apartment house replacing four small buildingsg No. 1060, in the southern half of the block, was opened in 1924. Compare with picture of
1060 at that time.
1928.
Joseph Smith, Photographer.
